coding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Cures-Robert-Smith-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Cures-Robert-Smith-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Cures-Robert-Smith-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Cures-Robert-Smith-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Cures-Robert-Smith-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Cures-Robert-Smith-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/The-Cure">Cure</a>的<a href="/artists/Robert-Smith">罗伯特·史密斯（Robert Smith）</a>开头，说明了为什么乐队的最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-review-lyrics-3801637">《迷失世界之歌》</a>几乎被称为“ Live from the Moon”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-review-lyrics-3801637">治愈 - “迷失世界的歌”：对损失的精通反思</a></strong></li></ul><p>摇滚偶像是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robert-smith-to-talk-through-the-cures-songs-of-a-lost-world-on-tims-listening-party-3817813">蒂姆·伯吉斯（Tim Burgess）的<em>蒂姆斯（Tims）听力派对</em>上的特别嘉宾</a>，他浏览了乐队著名的第14张录音室专辑。在聊天结束时，史密斯透露，LP的工作标题是“从月球上实时”，并讨论了月球着陆50周年的重要性影响了专辑的录制。</p><p> “这是月球着陆50周年，我小时候就迷恋了。我想成为一名足球运动员，但是如果我做不到，我想成为一名宇航员。我认为这有点像“如果我在足球比赛中失败，我会成为宇航员”，因为这就是世界的发展。我怎么错？”史密斯开始。 </p><p><iframe style="width: 100%; max-width: 660px; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 10px;" src="https://embed.podcasts.apple.com/no/podcast/the-cure/id1678973847?i=1000679693323" height="175" frameborder="0" sandbox="allow-forms allow-popups allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-storage-access-by-user-activation allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation"></iframe></p><p>他讲述了月球着陆的那天，以及他如何与家人站在外面，回忆道：“我记得我完全怀疑的感觉，被独自一人留在花园里。在电视上，所有颗粒状的黑白图像和东西都代表了月亮着陆。</p><p> “这是一个令人难以置信的事件，也是对一切，可能性，巨大的乐观感的感觉。我曾经抬头看着天空，以为“我要去月球。我经常以不同的形式编写该行，它代表了做任何您想做的事情的愿望。有点像“跟随你的梦想”，但这是真实的。”</p><p>然后，史密斯继续分享“迷失世界之歌”的工作标题是“月球直播”，并解释了他和乐队是如何在威尔士的Rockfield Studios重新创建1969年的1969年。当他们在2019年录制LP时。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DDVJz3BuFYK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 